---
title: Greek-Inspired Plant-Based Protein Shreds Salad with Olives and Feta
description: Is there anything better than a classic, creamy Greek dressing?! Tonight, Mediterranean-spiced plant-based protein shreds sit atop a Greek-inspired salad with peppers and tomatoes. Briny olives and feta cheese give the perfect salty hit!
